Well, if someone is doing this &quot;work&quot; as their sole source of income, I don&#39;t fault them, and there does seem to be a market, and no shortage of people seeking readings. 

 One thing is certain, no Moon==no boxes. It was Moon that got this technology/technique out in the public. Also worth mentioning is Bill Chappell, who came up with the hack version. 



 Frank-S



